name: Survive to Eat - The Game
description: The Player will interact with the world and eat different food types. Every type of food has different nutritional characteristics and there for it will change the characters nutrition and abilities to different levels. It will push his mind to think what to eat to jump higher, run faster and so on. There are four bars (for protein, carbs, fats, and happiness). The different nutrition sources will affect the single bar differently. He must deal with different effects based on the food he eats. The player will be pushed to do some kind of activities like jumping, climbing, crawling, swimming, … but he will need different bar levels for it.
